Package: tidyspark
Type: Package
Title: A Tidy Interface to Spark
Version: 0.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("S Daniel", "Zafar", email = "daniel.zafar@gmail.com", role = "cre"),
    person("Stern", "Eric", email = "eric.stern1@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: S Daniel Zafar <dan.zafar@databricks.com>
Description: Provides a familiar interface for Spark, following tidyverse 
    syntax. Designed to be easy to understand and contribute to. Also 
    implements the lower-level Spark API using pyspark-style R6 classes. 
